Package: petroreadr
Type: Package
Title: Read File Formats Used In The Oil Industry
Version: 0.2.1
Author: RavenRoad S.A.S.
Maintainer: Francesco Giorgetti <fg@ravenroadresources.com>
Description: This package include functions to read common file formats used in 
    the oil industry and converts them into datframes: .las for well logs, 
    ascii grid properties and .gslib grid properties. 
    More formats will be added with time.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
